title: Emergency Podcast: Reactions to the NBA Players' Strike
description:
Logan Murdock, Rob Mahoney, and Van Lathan share their real-time reactions to the NBA postponing Wednesday's games as a result of the player strike led by the Milwaukee Bucks.
